         "content_html" : "\n<p>Peter Jacksonâ€™s <em>Get Back</em> has, rightfully, been much-discussed. This essay by Ian Leslie, for his site The Ruffian, is one of my favorite takes. Chock full of keen observations. Perfect Sunday morning read.</p>\n\n<p class=\"x-netnewswire-hide\" style=\"padding-top: 1.5em;\"><em>Link: <strong><a href=\"https://ianleslie.substack.com/p/the-banality-of-genius-notes-on-peter\">ianleslie.substack.com/p/the-banality-of-genius-notes-onâ€¦</a></strong></em></p>\n"
